text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › No choppers here: Malcolm Turnbull ta... No choppers here: Malcolm Turnbull takes the train to Geelong Next Story Prev Story 4 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
How many train fares to Geelong can you get for a $5000 helicopter ride? More than 300 return trips, if you're travelling off peak. Malcolm Turnbull is well known for using public transport to get from A to B, and for letting the public know about it through social media. Start the conversation, or Read more at The Age.
